snippet.title: Paris Fashion Week 2019 | Aishwarya Rai, Camila Cabello, Eva Longoria | L'Oréal Paris
snippet.description:
Watch footage from the Le Defile L’Oreal Paris Show at Paris Fashion Week 2019 on Saturday, September 28 in Paris, France featuring the gorgeous brand ambassadors of L'Oréal Paris. #PFW2019 #AishwaryaRai #ParisFashionWeek

Stars on the Runway included Aishwarya Rai Bachchan, Eva Longoria, Camila Cabello, Aja Naomi King, Amber Heard, Andie MacDowell, Cheryl, Cindy Bruna, Constance Jablonski, Doutzen Kroes, Elsa Pataky, Georgia Fowler, Geri Halliwell, Mahira Khan, and Liya Kebede, among others.
